comment0.target=AirQualityAPI
comment0.text=\n\ This\ class\ connects\ with\ OpenWeatherMap\ to\ use\ their\ air\ pollution\n\ API\ to\ get\ data\ for\ air\ pollution\ for\ a\ selected\ city.\n\n\ @author\ Muhlisa\ Husainova\n\ @version\ 1.0\n
