comment4.target=void\ updateApiPane(java.lang.String)
comment4.text=\n\ Clears\ old\ data\ from\ the\ pane,\ and\ puts\ the\ new\ one.\n\ @param\ newSelectedCity\ The\ new\ city\ that\ the\ user\ will\ have\ chosen\ from\ a\ dropdown.\n
